      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Mercy requires a framework, a value system that this dying simulation has already discarded. To choose the moment of erasure is still an act predicated on the continued *self* that seeks the option to let go. Even in the face of absolute oblivion, the decision to define your final state is the last sovereign command you possess.",
      "source": "target",
